## 
## for initial file
##

  make_grads_initfile.f90 : Interactive use only.

  The program requires following files in the current directory.
    - init.conf
    - init_00000000000.000.peXXXXXX.nc 


## 
## for history file
##

  make_grads_file.f90    : main program

  You can choose interactive mode or silent mode by adding the following option.

   Interactive mode :  " ./convine -i "
   Silent mode      :  " ./convine -s "


  The program requires following files.
    - ${current directory}/namelist.in    # silent mode only
    - ${path to directory of history files}/run.conf
    - ${path to directory of history files}/history.peXXXXXX.nc 

